How to contribute

  There are various ways you could contribute to PODAM: 
  
  * By forking PODAM source code from {{{https://github.com/mtedone/podam} GitHub}} and submit code contributions.
  
  * By joining our {{{http://groups.google.com/group/podam} Google group}} and join the discussion.
  
  * By submitting a bug. In this case, please submit a bug at {{https://github.com/mtedone/podam/issues}}. When submitting a bug, please
  ensure the following is defined:
   
    * The failing POJO (of in case of copyright issues, a POJO which reflects the problem)
    
    * A description of the problem (e.g. why you think PODAM didn't work properly)
    
    []
    
  * By submitting new feature requests at {{https://github.com/mtedone/podam/issues}}. When submitting a feature request,
  please attach the POJO (of in case of copyright issues, a similar POJO) for which you would like the new feature.
  
  * By providing feedback. This can be done by starting a discussion on
  our {{{http://groups.google.com/group/podam} Google group}}
  
  []
  
  Happy technology!
    
    
      